5 Section 1. R.S. 30:1113 is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
6 §1113. Siting requirements
7 A. No Class VI injection wellhead shall be located within five hundred feet
8 of the following:
9 (1) Inhabited dwellings not owned by the storage operator or any owner in
10 interest bound by a contract with the storage operator that allows for location of a
11 Class VI injection well within five hundred feet of an inhabited dwelling.
12 (2) Schools.
13 (3) Healthcare facilities.
14 B. No pipeline for transport of carbon dioxide shall be constructed within
15 five hundred feet of the following:
16 (1) Inhabited dwellings.
