HB 589 Original 2026 Regular Session Farnum
Abstract: Adds a five hundred foot setback for construction of carbon dioxide transport
pipelines in certain areas.
Present law prohibits Class VI injection wellheads from being located within 500 ft. of
inhabited dwellings, schools, and healthcare facilities.
Proposed law retains present law and adds a prohibition for construction of pipelines for
transport of carbon dioxide within 500 ft. of inhabited dwellings, schools, and healthcare
facilities.
(Amends R.S. 30:1113)
